title: Stand Firm In Your "Yes" To God | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Stand Firm In Your "Yes" To God | Victoria Osteen
description:
What do you need to say yes to today? When you get in agreement with God, there’s no limit to what He can do in your life!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. 

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
